    <label>corrupt Republic starfleet</label>
    <description>An orbiting fleet of Republic naval cruisers dispatched to help resolve this planet's current crisis. This fleet follows the new administration's colonialist military doctrine, and shows great aggression in dealing with this planet's crisis and great disdain for its inhabitants. Much of this fleet's top brass from the Jedi Civil War have been replaced by political appointments, and it receives much of its funding from power-players in the Republic's core world nobility. This fleet is under strict orders to resolve this planet's crisis in the Republic's favor and to ensure its resources and wealth become property of the Republic.</description>
    <!-- <description>A growing Republic requires more and more resources to expand and improve the lives of its citizens, and far away on the lawless Rim, acquisition of those resources can only be guaranteed by the overwhelming force of the Republic Navy. Seeing the growing unrest on this critical world, a fleet of Republic warships has been dispatched to resolve this crisis in favor of the Republic. This Republic Starfleet wonâ€™t directly involve itself in the affairs of this planet, but will serve as a strong military presence to deter any outright coup against the ruling Planetary Militia. Its forces will generally remain in their planetside outposts, but will take swift action against any unknown element they deem a threat to their goals.</description> -->
